Hey guys, I was wondering if you can dynamically pull hubDB data into an email module using a contact's property?
For example:
```{% set contact_data = contact.branch %}
{% set table = hubdb_table_rows(&lt;db_id&gt;, 'name=' ~ contact_data) %}
{% for row in table %}
{{ row.name }}
{% endfor %}```
Using this logic doesn't seem to work when I make a test preview or send a test email.
